<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Welcome to Kilifonia Beauty</title>

<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');

body{
margin:0;
padding:0;
font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2);
}

.email-wrapper{
max-width:700px;
margin:40px auto;
background:#fff;
border-radius:20px;
overflow:hidden;
box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.15);
}

.header{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f093fb,#f5576c);
text-align:center;
padding:50px 30px;
color:white;
}

.logo{
max-width:180px;
border-radius:12px;
box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
}

.brand-name{
font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
font-size:28px;
font-weight:bold;
margin-top:15px;
}

.badge{
display:inline-block;
margin-top:20px;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#48bb78,#38a169);
padding:15px 30px;
border-radius:30px;
font-weight:bold;
animation:pulse 2s infinite;
}

.body{
padding:50px 40px;
}

h1{
font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;
text-align:center;
font-size:36px;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f093fb,#f5576c);
-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
}

.section{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8f9fa,#fff);
padding:30px;
border-radius:15px;
margin:35px 0;
border:1px solid #eee;
}

.cta{
display:inline-block;
padding:18px 45px;
border-radius:30px;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#667eea,#764ba2);
color:white;
font-weight:700;
text-decoration:none;
margin:15px;
box-shadow:0 8px 25px rgba(102,126,234,.4);
transition:.3s;
}

.cta:hover{
transform:translateY(-3px);
}

.footer{
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2d3748,#1a202c);
color:#a0aec0;
text-align:center;
padding:50px 30px;
}

.social a{
color:#a0aec0;
margin:0 12px;
text-decoration:none;
}

@keyframes pulse{
50%{transform:scale(1.05);}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="email-wrapper">

<div class="header">
<img class="logo"
src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dkdx7xytz/image/upload/v1772469610/blisslogo1_rwlktl.png"
/>

<div class="brand-name">Kilifonia Beauty</div>

<div class="badge">🎉 WELCOME TO THE DUBOIS FAMILY</div>
</div>

<div class="body">

<h1>Welcome to Luxury Skincare, <%= name %>!</h1>

<p style="text-align:center;font-size:18px;color:#4a5568;">
We are delighted to welcome you to Kilifonia Beauty where science meets luxury skincare.
Start your transformation journey with premium formulations designed for your skin.
</p>

<div class="section">
<h3 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;text-align:center">
✨ Personalized Skincare Experience
</h3>

<p style="color:#4a5568">
Receive expert skincare recommendations tailored to your skin type and concerns.
Enjoy science-backed formulations, luxury texture experience and visible results.
</p>
</div>

<div style="text-align:center">
<a href="https://kilifoniabeauty.co.ke/shop" class="cta">
Explore Collection
</a>

<a href="https://kilifoniabeauty.co.ke/skincare-timetable" class="cta"
style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f093fb,#f5576c)">
Create Skincare Timetable
</a>
</div>

</div>

<div class="footer">

<p>
<strong style="color:#f5576c">Kilifonia Beauty</strong><br>
Elevating Beauty Through Science and Nature
</p>

<div class="social">
<a href="https://kilifoniabeauty.co.ke">Website</a> |
<a href="https://instagram.com/kilifoniabeauty">Instagram</a> |
<a href="https://facebook.com/kilifoniabeauty">Facebook</a>
</div>

<p style="font-size:12px;margin-top:30px">
© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Kilifonia Beauty. All rights reserved.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>